sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as OPC UA client
    participant Endpoint as opcuapp Endpoint
    participant Server as OpcUaServer
    participant Conv as opcua_conversion
    participant Svc as SCADA service

    Client->>Endpoint: UA Binary request
    Endpoint->>Server: dispatch handler
    Server->>Conv: convert request payload
    Conv-->>Server: SCADA-native inputs
    Server->>Svc: Read / Write / Browse / Call / AddNodes / DeleteNodes
    Svc-->>Server: status + results
    Server->>Conv: convert results
    Conv-->>Server: OPC UA response payload
    Server-->>Endpoint: response
    Endpoint-->>Client: UA Binary response

    Note over Server,Svc: Monitored-item creation follows the same boundary:\nOpcUaServer adapts CreateMonitoredItem into\nscada::MonitoredItemService and wraps it back as\nan opcuapp monitored-item adapter.
